{"tid":470176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"８０間中學直播李飛　即場派卷考核計分","createTime":"2017-11-16T05:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T10:13:01.000Z","uid":141461,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f672383458496357f87d1d2e5e72605d3b2012c","tid":470176,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/130516_bd33ecf49496f1362e829160c566c8c7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F130516_bd33ecf49496f1362e829160c566c8c7.JPG&h=e2efc12a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會主任李飛今早(16日)出席在會展舉行的《基本法》研討會發表主題演講，題為「在國家憲法及《基本法》下香港作為國家特別行政區的角色及使命」，約80間中學於校園內直播李飛講話。其中一間參與的獅子會中學，約110名學生分別來自中三、中五及中六會在禮堂觀看直播。<br />\n<br />\n主辦學校以通識教育科「今日香港」課題，討論中國國家憲法及香港《基本法》的關係，每名學生手上有一張問卷考核計分，以及測試學生對憲法、《基本法》及一國兩制的認知程度。<br />\n<br />\n獅子會中學校長林日豐向學生指，如果今次課堂能引起同學對一國兩制的認識，以免被有心人士播獨。"},{"pid":"49a446336aadd7e6c38ba715ff182bf16d646bba","tid":470176,"uid":19501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"問吓牢牢掌握香港全面管治權，係邊一條基本法條文"},{"pid":"52e0b2caad1f74b67aa294768e99767ba48c6a6b","tid":470176,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a042a22593a3610fbdb18ccfdbef2b13307677","tid":470176,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a60d05ed9db8a6c3e6c881f156fa46a681ac29c","tid":470176,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6dd7701a1059b9ccc0578a2e557908eb24e79b","tid":470176,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:20:33.00